        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+2\n\nThis looks good. Good find of ch.vorburger.mariaDB4j.\n\nTesting this in sandbox here with updated mem VM: https://jenkins.onap.org/sandbox/job/ccsdk-sli-core-master-verify-java/2/console\nNote: I had to use ubuntu1604-basebuild-4c-4g instead of ubuntu1604-docker-2c-2g (which doesn't seem to exist, also there don't appear to be 2c-2g VMs to execute on).",
